{"tid":1374880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"目標零被捕，拖長戰線，慢慢煲","createTime":"2019-07-28T02:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T04:20:56.000Z","uid":290407,"like":16,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6e883d02ea8e77932af9970c91012610bfdc814f","tid":1374880,"uid":290407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:03:04.000Z","msg":"幾乎每次遊行集會我都有去，唔係走到最前但都會留到好夜，我有老婆仔女，如果冇負擔我都會走前D.<br />\n入正題，根據最近7月份既觀察:<br />\n<br />\n- 黑警將清場時間越推越早<br />\n- 遊行/示威完既1-2個鐘算係比較安全，過左呢段時間唔走就好高危<br />\n- 輿論已經開始對黑警亂用武力、示威者被毆、被捕開始麻木<br />\n- 最勇果班應該唔超過1000人, 每次都有數以十計手足被補，按咁推算，再過多一個月，軍力已經大減10-30%，9月開始學生又唔得閒，隨時成個運動就進入低潮<br />\n- 黎緊大型活動有8.31, 9.28??, 10.1<br />\n<br />\n係時候要退一退, 遊行/集會照出來但唔好同黑警撐咁耐, 可以衝/包既地方 (立法會/警總/中聯辦...)都試過了，民居地方更冇野值得衝/包，死守價值好低.  強調我係勇武和理非都支持, 只係呢個moment我覺得唔適合太勇武。<br />\n<br />\n要轉一轉mode, 諗下D新idea, keep住民情, 引起外媒注意, 要諗新計.<br />\n以下係一D提議: (部份係之前手足's idea)<br />\n- 手挽手慢步遊行<br />\n- 入夜後全場用手機banner app顯示同一個口號 (夠一千人做已經好L震撼!!!)<br />\n   (7.27機場集會唔少巴絲打有用，好搶眼，用tablet更佳)<br />\nBanner app (iOS): <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/led-banner-scrolling-text/id1356029756?fbclid=IwAR3QzJIb5OhEyWlpQHeR9EcN58N6IAeCmaJOT7OaHGuNENfY6FS4CU7ZiAo&amp;l=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fled-banner-scrolling-text%2Fid1356029756%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3QzJIb5OhEyWlpQHeR9EcN58N6IAeCmaJOT7OaHGuNENfY6FS4CU7ZiAo%26l%3Den&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F13HDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=d48e3f69\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/led-banner-scrolling-text/id1356029756?fbclid=IwAR3QzJIb5OhEyWlpQHeR9EcN58N6IAeCmaJOT7OaHGuNENfY6FS4CU7ZiAo&amp;l=en</a><br />\nBanner app (Android): <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=oops.ledscroller&amp;fbclid=IwAR2XjBA9Ve-uOi9HiYVqsbv1ZVZe8NaYiRNUYNoGtaFF1fAjUPXWY4se1L0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Doops.ledscroller%26fbclid%3DIwAR2XjBA9Ve-uOi9HiYVqsbv1ZVZe8NaYiRNUYNoGtaFF1fAjUPXWY4se1L0&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F13HDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=51ecbfe4\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=oops.ledscroller&amp;fbclid=IwAR2XjBA9Ve-uOi9HiYVqsbv1ZVZe8NaYiRNUYNoGtaFF1fAjUPXWY4se1L0</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oBr2yz7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoBr2yz7.png&h=7715f332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n- 行行下全體靜坐<br />\n- 集體行為藝術 (90%人扮黑警，10%人扮示威者) / 跳舞"},{"pid":"853546cd37f394957261098b78d140d9055f3fd7","tid":1374880,"uid":11698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:11:15.000Z","msg":"有一個抗爭未試過，就係朝早730交通銀行/ifc金管局呢啲地方聚人，快閃佔中，點睇"},{"pid":"5097eea14bb771944c9d9e816c0f0ed73d2e28c0","tid":1374880,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:28:30.000Z","msg":"「長文」抗爭除Be Water外，Assassin's Creed嘅信條你都一定要識！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1374405\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1374405</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"756f60d3f21cdc9f58449f83f3283f255caebbde","tid":1374880,"uid":88823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:30:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8e3555af7cadaa1a9073f062cb9e94b5bd7c9df5","tid":1374880,"uid":256131,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:36:07.000Z","msg":"如果叫口號舉banner有用<br />\n有邊個想勇武？"},{"pid":"7ca612ce70ae78a37ea555c1223a8fee66aa9040","tid":1374880,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:38:15.000Z","msg":"［需共識］齊上齊落 vs 自主撤水（集中討論）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1374867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1374867</a>"},{"pid":"58209549ebe745f387102efe1711890a8ca77fda","tid":1374880,"uid":290407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8e3555af7cadaa1a9073f062cb9e94b5bd7c9df5","tid":1374880,"uid":256131,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:36:07.000Z","msg":"如果叫口號舉banner有用<br />\n有邊個想勇武？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:13:26.000Z","msg":"重點唔係否定勇武，從來我都覺得和理非同勇武係相輔相成，如果冇6.9就冇6.12，冇6.12就未必有6.16...<br />\n<br />\n冇野係絕對有用或冇用，係有幾多用。無論和理非和勇武，如果形式唔變，功效係會慢慢diminish架。<br />\n<br />\n係人數有限情況下，諗多d idea去catch attention，keep住民情係好重要，黎緊選舉民情冷卻就死得。<br />\n<br />\n如果勇武方面有咩新idea都歡迎提議! 不過我諗唔到。"},{"pid":"3bc35e0cdb6c633d4c0083644ee3d59114909523","tid":1374880,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:15:38.000Z","msg":"每次傷廿幾三十個 ， 就算唔拉， 點拖長？"},{"pid":"c569617aeb017d927797d0c3d432b77e8ba396de","tid":1374880,"uid":290407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"853546cd37f394957261098b78d140d9055f3fd7","tid":1374880,"uid":11698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:11:15.000Z","msg":"有一個抗爭未試過，就係朝早730交通銀行/ifc金管局呢啲地方聚人，快閃佔中，點睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:16:02.000Z","msg":"首先要夠人多，人少黑警做野快到你唔信。<br />\n快閃可以。"},{"pid":"960ec1aa8fb654ff2b31af6847d50f0452b60ac6","tid":1374880,"uid":288765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:18:46.000Z","msg":"今日中環見"},{"pid":"6ebfec75707c9d3a208c374f744d66a428b8a636","tid":1374880,"uid":290407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bc35e0cdb6c633d4c0083644ee3d59114909523","tid":1374880,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:15:38.000Z","msg":"每次傷廿幾三十個 ， 就算唔拉， 點拖長？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:20:56.000Z","msg":"所以真係要諗諗，再咁落去可以維持到幾耐。<br />\n黑警既惡行全世界都睇到，民意我地贏晒，短期冇必要同死差佬對峙。"}]}